  <Dialog id="0" name="MSG_000_0_0" type="Message">
    <Page spk="0000"><![CDATA[{f 0 5 254}{f 2 1}{f 4 5 2 2 51 -1 0 0}{f 3 1 1 0 0 1 0 0}{f 4 23 0 1 2 25 25}See? That's what happens when you don't listen![n]{f 1 1}]]></Page>
    <Page spk="0000"><![CDATA[{f 0 5 254}{f 2 1}{f 4 5 2 3 51 -1 0 0}{f 3 1 1 0 0 2 0 0}{f 4 23 0 1 3 25 25}Well... Are you okay?[n]{f 1 1}]]></Page>
  </Dialog>
  <Dialog id="1" name="MSG_001_0_0" type="Message">
    <Page spk="0001"><![CDATA[{f 0 5 254}{f 2 1}{f 4 5 3 10 51 -1 0 0}{f 3 1 1 0 0 3 0 0}O-Of course I am![n]{f 1 1}]]></Page>
    <Page spk="0001"><![CDATA[{f 0 5 254}{f 2 1}{f 4 5 3 10 51 -1 0 0}{f 3 1 1 0 0 4 0 0}I was doin' just fine...[n]{f 1 1}]]></Page>
  </Dialog>
  <Dialog id="2" name="MSG_002_0_0" type="Message">
    <Page spk="0000"><![CDATA[{f 0 5 254}{f 2 1}{f 4 5 2 2 51 -1 0 0}{f 3 1 1 0 0 5 0 0}{f 4 23 0 1 2 25 25}Hey, what's your problem?[n]{f 1 1}]]></Page>
  </Dialog>
  <Dialog id="3" name="MSG_003_0_0" type="Message">
    <Page spk="0002"><![CDATA[{f 0 5 254}{f 2 1}{f 4 5 5 2 51 50 0 0}{f 3 1 1 0 0 6 0 0}Be careful, you three![n]{f 1 1}]]></Page>
    <Page spk="0002"><![CDATA[{f 0 5 254}{f 2 1}{f 4 5 5 2 51 50 0 0}{f 3 1 1 0 0 7 0 0}I don't detect any movement, but stay alert![n]{f 1 1}]]></Page>
  </Dialog>
  <Dialog id="4" name="MSG_004_0_0" type="Message">
    <Page spk="0001"><![CDATA[{f 0 5 254}{f 2 1}{f 4 5 3 4 51 -1 0 0}{f 3 1 1 0 0 8 0 0}{f 4 23 0 2 4 25 25}Whoa, what the—!? Why're we moving!?[n]{f 1 1}]]></Page>
  </Dialog>
  <Dialog id="5" name="MSG_005_0_0" type="Message">
    <Page spk="0002"><![CDATA[{f 0 5 254}{f 2 1}{f 4 5 5 0 51 50 0 0}{f 3 1 1 0 0 9 0 0}It looks like the entire monorail is under the Shadow's control...[n]{f 1 1}]]></Page>
  </Dialog>
  <Dialog id="6" name="MSG_006_0_0" type="Message">
    <Page spk="0000"><![CDATA[{f 0 5 254}{f 2 1}{f 4 5 2 3 51 -1 0 0}{f 3 1 1 0 0 10 0 0}{f 4 23 0 1 3 25 25}What? Is that really okay!?[n]{f 1 1}]]></Page>
  </Dialog>
  <Dialog id="7" name="MSG_007_0_0" type="Message">
    <Page spk="0001"><![CDATA[{f 0 5 254}{f 2 1}{f 4 5 3 3 51 -1 0 0}{f 3 1 1 0 0 11 0 0}{f 4 23 0 2 3 25 25}Uh... This doesn't look good.[n]{f 1 1}]]></Page>
  </Dialog>
  <Dialog id="8" name="MSG_008_0_0" type="Message">
    <Page spk="0002"><![CDATA[{f 0 5 254}{f 2 1}{f 4 5 5 4 51 50 0 0}{f 3 1 1 0 0 12 0 0}If we don't stop it, it's going to crash into the next train![n]{f 1 1}]]></Page>
  </Dialog>
  <Dialog id="9" name="MSG_008_5_0" type="Message">
    <Page spk="0002"><![CDATA[{f 0 5 254}{f 2 1}{f 4 17 2 4 1}]]></Page>
  </Dialog>
  <Dialog id="10" name="MSG_009_0_0" type="Message">
    <Page spk="0000"><![CDATA[{f 0 5 254}{f 2 1}{f 4 5 2 4 51 -1 0 0}{f 3 1 1 0 0 13 0 0}{f 4 23 0 1 4 25 25}Crash!?[n]{f 1 1}]]></Page>
    <Page spk="0000"><![CDATA[{f 0 5 254}{f 2 1}{f 4 5 2 4 51 -1 0 0}{f 3 1 1 0 0 14 0 0}{f 4 23 0 1 4 25 25}Hey, what are we gonna do!?[n]{f 1 1}]]></Page>
  </Dialog>
  <Dialog id="11" name="MSG_010_0_0" type="Message">
    <Page spk="0002"><![CDATA[{f 0 5 254}{f 2 1}{f 4 5 5 0 51 50 0 0}{f 3 1 1 0 0 15 0 0}Calm down and listen.[n]{f 1 1}]]></Page>
    <Page spk="0002"><![CDATA[{f 0 5 254}{f 2 1}{f 4 5 5 0 51 50 0 0}{f 3 1 1 0 0 16 0 0}I detect a powerful reading in the front car. That must be our target.[n]{f 1 1}]]></Page>
    <Page spk="0002"><![CDATA[{f 0 5 254}{f 2 1}{f 4 5 5 0 51 50 0 0}{f 3 1 1 0 0 17 0 0}You'll have to defeat that to stop the runaway train![n]{f 1 1}]]></Page>
  </Dialog>
  <Dialog id="12" name="MSG_011_0_0" type="Message">
    <Page spk="0001"><![CDATA[{f 0 5 254}{f 2 1}{f 4 5 3 2 51 -1 0 0}{f 3 1 1 0 0 18 0 0}{f 4 23 0 2 2 25 25}Crap! What kind of messed up ride is this!?[n]{f 1 1}]]></Page>
  </Dialog>
